Invocation Name: gas giants
des:
The gas giants of our solar system are huge? Do you some of their features? What are they made of? Take this family friendly quiz to find out. If you're right, reward yourself with a prize (a jelly bean or an apple). If you're wrong, you can always try again.

Let us know how you do and have fun testing some basic facts about the gas giants.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
